# Intelligent Personal Assistant

This project implements a simple intelligent personal assistant using Python, speech recognition, and natural language processing.

## Features

- Speech recognition using Google's Speech Recognition API
- Text processing with NLTK (Natural Language Toolkit)
- Sentiment analysis using TextBlob
- Basic command execution (time and weather commands)

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/personal-assistant.git
   cd personal-assistant
Install dependencies:

2. Install Dependencies

'''bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run the script:

'''bash
python personal_assistant.py

3. Speak a command and see the assistant in action!
